---
title: Double-Stacked BBQ Burgers with Spiced Sweet Potatoes and Pickles
description: Slow and smoky bbq in one speedy bite! Flavourful double-stacked beef burgers loaded with lots of bbq sauce and classic dill pickles! All of the kiddos' favourite flavours... with a bit of spring mix for good measure.
